  "narrative": "# Turn 48\n\n*7 commanders issued orders this turn.*\n\n## Strategic Decisions\n\n### CURATOR (artifact collector)\n\nDispatched 4 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W25, W25, W25, W19.\n\n### NOMAD (merchant)\n\nDispatched 3 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W19, W19, W9.\n\n### PROPHET (apostle)\n\nEconomic activity: loaded cargo onto 1 fleets; unloaded at 2 destinations; commissioned 8 new ships.\n\n### REAVER (pirate)\n\nDispatched 4 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W26, W16, W13, W3.\n\n### SOLARIS (empire builder)\n\nDispatched 2 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W27, W3.\n\nEconomic activity: unloaded at 1 destinations; commissioned 6 new ships; invested in 3 units of industry.\n\n### TERRAN (empire builder)\n\nDispatched 2 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W12, W30.\n\nEconomic activity: invested in 1 units of industry.\n\n### TRADER (merchant)\n\nDispatched 2 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W11, W22.\n\nEconomic activity: commissioned 3 new ships.\n\n## Consequences\n\n### Territorial Shifts\n\n- **NOMAD** seized control of W19 (previously TRADER).\n\n- **TERRAN** seized control of W30 (previously SOLARIS).\n\n### Fleet Movements\n\n- **CURATOR** moved: F7\u2192W25, F8\u2192W25\n\n- **NOMAD** moved: F15\u2192W19, F16\u2192W9\n\n- **REAVER** repositioned 4 fleets across the sector.\n\n- **SOLARIS** moved: F1\u2192W27, F2\u2192W3\n\n- **TERRAN** moved: F13\u2192W12, F14\u2192W30\n\n- **TRADER** moved: F3\u2192W11, F4\u2192W22\n\n### Production\n\n- **PROPHET** launched 8 new ships.\n\n- **SOLARIS** launched 6 new ships.\n\n- **TRADER** launched 3 new ships.\n\n- **SOLARIS** built 3 industry.\n\n- **TERRAN** built 1 industry.\n"
